{"type":null,"faqId":9475,"title":"荣耀X1（7D-501u）7.0   打开 WLAN，如果搜不到网络，耗电量仍会比较大，为什么？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">搜索上默认的休眠策略是永不休眠，即如果没有可连接的</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络，</span><span>WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">也只是进入低功耗模式，其芯片仍在工作，所以耗电量会比较快；只有在关闭屏幕十几分钟后，</span><span>WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">芯片才会停止搜索并自动断电。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29932\" /><span style=\"color:#339966;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">建议您在</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">搜索不到网络时，手动关闭</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">以节约电量。</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"75","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396253418000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":131,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}